N
N
 E[N] = \underbrace{1}_{1st\ coin\ flip} + \underbrace{\alpha}_{prob.\ it\ fails}\cdot \underbrace{E[N]}_{expected\ \#\ of\ further\ flips} 
E[N]=(1-α)\cdot1+α(1+Ε[Ν])=1-α+α+α\cdotΕ[Ν]=1+α\cdotΕ[Ν]
\begin{align*}E[N]&=E_X\left[E_{N|X}[N|X]\right]=P(X=H)E[N|X=H]+P(X=T)E[N|X=T]=\\&=(1-α)\cdot1+α\cdot(1+E[N])=1+α\cdot E[N]\end{align*}
